
To treba izbrisati. `.gitignore` ne sme da ima markdown ogradu.

Stavi ovakav `.gitignore`:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python

venv/
.venv/
env/
backend/venv/
backend/.venv/

*.log

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
backend/.env
frontend/.env
frontend/.env.local
!.env.example

# Node / Vue
node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
frontend/dist/
*.local

# Database / local storage
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
postgres-data/
pgdata/
database/data/

# Uploaded / generated datasets
uploads/
backend/uploads/
ml/datasets/uploads/
ml/outputs/*
!ml/outputs/.gitkeep

# Local data files
backend/app/data/*.csv
!backend/app/data/.gitkeep

# System
.DS_Store
__MACOSX/
__MACOSX__/

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml